{"tid":1512743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"街坊可唔可以入一入嚟 我有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-08-28T04:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T04:29:21.000Z","uid":310853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"baaca5a8bec40454fd73137ba4604fc0726a5966","tid":1512743,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:16:16.000Z","msg":"首先 我係P牌 但我唔係冷軍<br />\n雖然依句冇乜人理 我知<br />\n我見好多人屌人話送頭<br />\n亦都好多人話點解唔屌警察屌街坊<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家可唔可以唔好以為街坊身分就冇事</span><br />\n警察濫捕係好唔合理 直頭係仆街<br />\n我自己都係街坊 都有被追過 有跑走<br />\n的而且確 依加濫捕係事實<br />\n我都好嬲 點解我係街坊落樓要差d比人拉<br />\n<br />\n但係 今時今日都仲可以聽到<br />\n「我街坊嚟㗎 怕乜姐」<br />\n「個街坊企定定比人拉咗」<br />\n<br />\n我唔係叫大家唔落樓唔出街<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係想大家有返d危機意識</span><br />\n佢哋已經癲咗㗎喇<br />\n街坊就算乜都冇做都照拉<br />\n「有人會話都告唔入 怕咩」<br />\n48小時係咪代價?<br />\n佢會唔會老屈你?<br />\n佢會唔會暗地裡郁手?<br />\n佢哋會唔會出埋d暗招?<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫散水<br />\n係佢哋直逼到面前時<br />\n去到真係真係守唔住時<br />\n求下你哋真係要跑啦<br />\n唔好再企定定<br />\n<br />\n係會有犧牲 我明<br />\n革命係有血有汗有付出<br />\n但我希望大家減少陣亡"},{"pid":"1a67d4f6dfeaee963b7442fb8595d7423d1f6d85","tid":1512743,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=bbaa21af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=d2aa7403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-u